  - 3-Year Cost: $1,960
- Traditional:
  - Initial: $1,600
  - Electricity (197W, 6h/day): 1,294.29 kWh × $0.15 = $194.13
  - 3-Year Cost: $1,794.13
- Difference: $1,960 - $1,794.13 = $165.87
